EarlyStage
  Author:  Globox_Z
  Source:  https://github.com/Globox1997/EarlyStage
  Modrinth: https://modrinth.com/mod/earlystage
  CurseForge: https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/earlystage
  License: MIT
  Notes:   Heavily modified for NeoForge 1.21.1. Most of the original feature
           set has been cut, rewritten, or restyled — the surviving pieces are
           the rock world feature, sieve mechanic, crafting rock workbench,
           flint tools, the EXTRA_BLASTING-related code is removed, all bark
           items removed, all buckets removed, all steel content removed,
           wooden shield/stone shears removed, ModMenu/Cloth-Config integration
           replaced with NeoForge ModConfigSpec, EMI integration dropped,
           deep blast-furnace mixins dropped, beginner-death-count system
           dropped. Mappings translated from Yarn to Mojmap+Parchment.

Never Punching Trees
  Author:  96_Leaf
  Source:  https://github.com/96Leaf/NeverPunchingTrees
  CurseForge: https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/never-punching-trees
  License: MIT
  Notes:   Block-breaking restriction logic ported and adapted. Tag namespace
           consolidated under rough_beginnings: instead of neverpunchingtrees:.
           Default breakable/canbreak tag values revised; mud, packed_mud,
           muddy_mangrove_roots, and moss_block now hand-breakable for
           consistency with the rest of the dirt family.

